00:00:01.070 --> 00:00:05.460
This course is designed to prepare leaders who may take up

00:00:05.460 --> 00:00:09.900
a leadership position over data science initiatives at their companies.

00:00:09.900 --> 00:00:12.360
For leaders assuming a new role,

00:00:12.360 --> 00:00:18.555
it is common to be asked to prepare a plan for the first 100 days in the new job.

00:00:18.555 --> 00:00:21.000
As a student in this course,

00:00:21.000 --> 00:00:25.320
you'll prepare that 100 day data science plan for a company of your choosing.

00:00:25.320 --> 00:00:29.280
This could be your current company or some other existing company.

00:00:29.280 --> 00:00:31.020
As part of this project,

00:00:31.020 --> 00:00:33.480
you will build the following: an

00:00:33.480 --> 00:00:37.835
Identification of six data science opportunities for the organization,

00:00:37.835 --> 00:00:41.200
a prioritization of these opportunities,

00:00:41.200 --> 00:00:45.200
the human capital plan for your data science organization,

00:00:45.200 --> 00:00:51.100
a data and data architecture strategy, machine learning architecture.

00:00:51.100 --> 00:00:56.960
The work product for this capstone project will be a detailed presentation to the CEO,

00:00:56.960 --> 00:01:01.590
detailing your plan and the rationale behind your decisions.

